cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper deals with planar object tracking, which is a problem in computer vision and robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper involves evaluation of state-of-the-art algorithms, which falls under the category of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of robotics also suggests the category of robotics and automation (cs.RO). The paper also involves detailed analysis of the evaluation results, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper involves video sequences, which suggests the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
